1
00:00:14,898 --> 00:00:17,795
♪ Beautiful love ♪

2
00:00:18,033 --> 00:00:20,877
♪ When you find it ♪

3
00:00:21,588 --> 00:00:25,732
♪ You try to embrace it ♪

4
00:00:27,574 --> 00:00:30,684
♪ You dedicate to it ♪

5
00:00:30,769 --> 00:00:33,476
♪ You give it your all ♪

6
00:00:34,197 --> 00:00:39,044
♪ So that it lasts forever ♪

7
00:00:39,317 --> 00:00:42,590
♪ But sometimes
it turns into darkness ♪

8
00:00:42,601 --> 00:00:45,644
♪ If you love so much
that it blinds you ♪

9
00:00:46,100 --> 00:00:50,967
♪ Beauty can turn into pain ♪

10
00:00:51,474 --> 00:00:57,747
♪ If love ends in vengeance ♪

11
00:00:58,814 --> 00:01:03,061
♪ Will you still embrace it? ♪

12
00:01:04,030 --> 00:01:10,893
♪ If love is gained
in exchange for someone's life ♪

13
00:01:11,342 --> 00:01:19,412
♪ Will you still say this love
is what you wanted? ♪

