295
00:23:22,275 --> 00:23:23,436
bastards like you

296
00:23:23,572 --> 00:23:26,345
can't survive outside the palace,

297
00:23:26,563 --> 00:23:28,429
so you're always damn eager to please.

298
00:23:28,874 --> 00:23:30,017
