299
00:23:30,031 --> 00:23:31,710
to work in the same palace as us.

300
00:23:32,412 --> 00:23:33,412
As for us,

301
00:23:33,492 --> 00:23:35,429
we don't want to be friends with you.

302
00:23:35,815 --> 00:23:37,881
