307
00:24:14,682 --> 00:24:16,799
Daughter of the Eastern Trade Minister.

308
00:24:18,093 --> 00:24:19,167
I'm Malai.

309
00:24:21,541 --> 00:24:23,027
I saw you being bullied.

310
00:24:23,135 --> 00:24:25,054
So I came over to check on you.

311
00:24:25,814 --> 00:24:26,814
Look at you

312
00:24:27,149 --> 00:24:29,022
bawling your pretty eyes out.

313
00:24:30,664 --> 00:24:31,664
I don't get it.

314
00:24:31,945 --> 00:24:33,023
Why did you just

315
00:24:33,359 --> 00:24:35,149
let them walk all over you like that?

316
00:24:35,533 --> 00:24:36,533
It's nothing.

317
00:24:37,534 --> 00:24:39,626
They come from noble lineage,

318
00:24:41,065 --> 00:24:42,245
while I,

319
00:24:42,999 --> 00:24:44,184
am just a bastard.

320
00:24:44,537 --> 00:24:45,736
Mother died at my birth.

321
00:24:46,843 --> 00:24:48,323
Father ignores me,

322
00:24:49,103 --> 00:24:50,489
