Follow me.

329
00:25:08,821 --> 00:25:10,608
I'll show you something good.

330
00:25:13,386 --> 00:25:15,201
Then why are you taking my lowly self

331
00:25:15,226 --> 00:25:16,168
as your mistress?

332
00:25:18,551 --> 00:25:20,438
Since we're husband and wife,

333
00:25:20,463 --> 00:25:23,219
we should confide in each other, right?

334
00:25:23,898 --> 00:25:25,734
If you weren't so close with Dech,

335
00:25:25,919 --> 00:25:28,265
you'd have been kicked out long ago!

