371
00:27:26,603 --> 00:27:28,525
Crazy bitch!

372
00:27:40,772 --> 00:27:41,772
You harlot!

373
00:27:42,913 --> 00:27:44,311
Ms. Bu-nga!

374
00:27:44,972 --> 00:27:46,965
