408
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:21,066
and live with no regrets.

409
00:29:24,227 --> 00:29:25,733
I'm so grateful, Bu-nga.

410
00:29:27,543 --> 00:29:29,663
I'll strive to be braver.

411
00:29:31,185 --> 00:29:32,424
I'd be content with just

412
00:29:32,445 --> 00:29:34,238
