424
00:31:52,329 --> 00:31:54,009
You were gone for days.

425
00:31:55,127 --> 00:31:56,361
Wouldn't be surprised if you

426
00:31:56,386 --> 00:31:57,992
were merry with someone else.

427
00:32:05,756 --> 00:32:07,948
How could that be possible

428
00:32:08,992 --> 00:32:10,032
when my heart

429
00:32:10,824 --> 00:32:11,912
belongs entirely to you?

430
00:32:14,560 --> 00:32:16,031
