435
00:32:51,334 --> 00:32:52,716
Is something bothering you?

436
00:32:56,118 --> 00:32:57,257
Are you not happy,

437
00:32:58,279 --> 00:32:59,408
even though I am here?

438
00:33:00,323 --> 00:33:01,443
It's not like that.

439
00:33:03,330 --> 00:33:04,330
I...

440
00:33:05,142 --> 00:33:07,349
I'm very happy I get to see you, Dech.

441
00:33:11,388 --> 00:33:12,523
I just wonder

442
00:33:12,930 --> 00:33:15,397
