444
00:33:19,256 --> 00:33:21,056
Do you trust me, Ms. Malai?

445
00:33:29,945 --> 00:33:30,945
I do.

446
00:33:31,992 --> 00:33:33,227
I have more faith in you

447
00:33:34,623 --> 00:33:36,172
than in anyone else in this world.

448
00:33:36,808 --> 00:33:37,808
Have patience.

449
00:33:39,925 --> 00:33:41,045
I promise you that

450
00:33:42,243 --> 00:33:44,792
we'll soon be together openly,

451
00:33:46,187 --> 00:33:47,299
without any harassment

452
00:33:47,728 --> 00:33:50,103
from the Viscount or Ms. Ramphoei.

453
00:33:50,969 --> 00:33:53,009
I don't know when it will come true

454
00:33:53,850 --> 00:33:54,884
or what...

455
00:33:55,748 --> 00:33:57,002
your plans may be.

456
00:34:00,121 --> 00:34:01,131
But I...

457
00:34:01,402 --> 00:34:02,442
I'm confident

458
00:34:03,343 --> 00:34:04,645
I'm confident that you'll...

459
00:34:05,364 --> 00:34:06,964
you'll keep your word

460
00:34:08,834 --> 00:34:11,123
