461
00:34:14,764 --> 00:34:16,190
Thank you so much, Ms. Malai.

462
00:35:16,749 --> 00:35:18,370
Have you no shame, my lord?

463
00:35:18,805 --> 00:35:19,927
Continuing to visit a man

464
00:35:19,928 --> 00:35:21,024
who doesn't love you.

465
00:35:23,080 --> 00:35:24,950
You've been talking too much lately.

466
00:35:25,305 --> 00:35:26,305
Just a servant,

467
00:35:26,459 --> 00:35:27,464
