470
00:35:38,567 --> 00:35:40,454
Since we're husband and wife,

471
00:35:40,479 --> 00:35:43,235
we should confide in each other, right?

472
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:45,756
If you weren't so close with Dech,

473
00:35:45,909 --> 00:35:48,255
you'd have been kicked out long ago!

